01:09.570 --> 01:11.571
Oh, yeah.

02:35.239 --> 02:38.199
Sir, l know l'm not supposed
to ask questions...

02:38.367 --> 02:39.700
...but who are you?

02:43.914 --> 02:46.415
No one you wanna know, kid.

03:08.063 --> 03:10.231
Looks like someone had a bad day.

03:15.028 --> 03:18.239
Copy.
We're still searching for any survivors.

03:22.244 --> 03:25.079
lt happened about four hours ago,
just before dawn.

03:25.247 --> 03:28.833
The creature was sighted
crossing the U.S.-Canadian border.

03:29.001 --> 03:32.128
