when it reached civilization.

03:32.296 --> 03:33.671
Creature?

03:33.839 --> 03:38.217
The Americans call it "the Hulk."
lntel's sketchy.

03:38.385 --> 03:41.596
Department H thinks the U.S. military
is covering something up.

03:59.156 --> 04:01.908
lt smells toxic.

04:02.451 --> 04:03.951
Gunpowder too.

04:04.119 --> 04:07.622
WelI, someone tried to fight back.

04:11.752 --> 04:13.836
Guess they didn't fight hard enough.

04:14.004 --> 04:16.339
Department H wants you to find
and stop the Hulk. ..

04:16.505 --> 04:18.673
...before he reaches another town
or city.

04:19.051 --> 04:21.010
And if you can't stop it, kiIl it.

04:23.055 --> 04:25.514
Sounds Iike fun.

04:39.029 --> 04:41.197
Sir, l think we got something.

04:46.620 --> 04:50.581
-Do you want us to try for a landing?
-Don't bother.

06:45.489 --> 06:47.448
What--? What was that?

06:48.492 --> 06:49.658
Hey, bub.

06:52.162 --> 06:56.457
You haven't seen a big monster
running around anywhere, have you?

06:57.250 --> 06:58.834
No. Stay back.

06:59.002 --> 07:02.213
Stay away from me. Stay back.

07:03.965 --> 07:08.177
Relax, crybaby. I ain't gonna--

07:12.182 --> 07:14.183
You smell toxic.

07:20.524 --> 07:22.358
Who are you?

07:22.526 --> 07:25.986
Please, l'm begging you,
leave me alone.

07:26.154 --> 07:30.491
For your own sake, please, go.
You're in terrible danger.

07:33.954 --> 07:35.955
Here's the deal, misty.

07:36.123 --> 07:38.040
There's a third claw
that's gonna come out...

07:38.208 --> 07:39.500
...if you don't start talking.

07:57.561 --> 07:59.562
Oh, heIl.

08:00.063 --> 08:02.898
l don't suppose you got any interest
in talking this out.

08:17.497 --> 08:19.373
What the hell happened?

08:26.506 --> 08:28.716
Oh, yeah.

08:30.594 --> 08:32.553
Let's do this.

08:33.263 --> 08:34.429
Come on.

09:44.584 --> 09:47.002
Hulk smash little man.

09:47.170 --> 09:51.715
Little man, leave Hulk alone.

09:54.302 --> 10:00.099
Hulk is strongest there is!

10:32.465 --> 10:37.469
Okay, bub. Let's try that again.

11:26.353 --> 11:27.895
Thanks, runt.

11:28.063 --> 11:31.023
We've been trying to take him down
for weeks.

11:31.191 --> 11:34.109
Logan, buddy, it's me, Deadpool.

11:34.277 --> 11:36.862
l shot you.

11:51.628 --> 11:53.462
What are you looking at?

11:59.719 --> 12:03.806
Prepare the lab. We're on our way.

12:07.977 --> 12:11.438
His vital signs are increasing.
He's waking up.

12:18.154 --> 12:22.324
Now, Miss Hines, begin
the adamantium bonding process.

12:22.492 --> 12:24.952
-Yes, professor.
-Commencing infusion.

12:34.045 --> 12:37.089
-His vitals are erratic but holding.
-Excellent.

12:37.257 --> 12:40.092
lncrease to maximum.

13:16.129 --> 13:20.382
