l know him. He can't be controlled.

13:38.359 --> 13:41.069
You have his DNA,
so just let me kill him.

13:41.237 --> 13:44.781
l'll take that under advisement,
Sabretooth.

13:44.949 --> 13:49.328
-Prepare your team for the mission.
-Your funeral.

14:01.257 --> 14:05.594
What do you say after the mission,
we kill all those floating babies?

14:05.762 --> 14:08.180
Do you ever shut up, Wilson?

14:08.765 --> 14:11.767
What? Babies creep me out.

14:19.651 --> 14:21.902
He's fighting the programming.

14:22.779 --> 14:26.281
We are losing control.
lncrease the dosage.

14:26.449 --> 14:31.036
lnitiate lockdown procedures.
And someone activate Sabretooth.

14:37.710 --> 14:40.671
Guards! Guards!

15:12.036 --> 15:15.038
Wakey-wakey time.

15:15.999 --> 15:18.625
Logan, we missed you.

15:18.793 --> 15:21.336
And Weapon X just hasn't been
the same without you.

15:21.504 --> 15:23.922
Nobody calIs me "bub" anymore.

15:24.090 --> 15:26.341
And Omega Red's a bed wetter.

15:28.511 --> 15:33.473
One day l will tear out
your flippant tongue, Wilson.

15:34.642 --> 15:37.060
He's very ashamed.

15:37.854 --> 15:40.063
Despite Deadpool's idiocy...

15:40.231 --> 15:43.817
...Weapon X is indeed pleased
to have you back, Logan.

15:43.985 --> 15:46.778
We put considerable time
and money into you.

15:46.946 --> 15:48.322
And pointy things.

15:48.489 --> 15:51.533
You were our best operative,
Wolverine.

15:51.701 --> 15:53.827
So disappointing.

15:53.995 --> 15:56.038
But you did lead us to Dr. Banner.

15:56.205 --> 16:00.042
Of course,
you know him better as the Hulk.

16:00.209 --> 16:02.377
l shot him in the ass.
With one of these.

16:03.504 --> 16:05.047
What? I did.

16:05.214 --> 16:08.550
Weapon X has been pursuing the Hulk
for weeks.

16:26.319 --> 16:30.364
Unfortunately,
there was some collateral damage.

16:30.531 --> 16:33.825
lf only Department H
had sent you in sooner.. .

16:33.993 --> 16:37.579
...who knows how much destruction
could have been avoided?

16:37.747 --> 16:39.706
What do you want with the Hulk?

16:40.083 --> 16:42.751
We just wanna help him
find his happy place.

16:42.919 --> 16:44.628
Did you see how angry he was?

16:44.796 --> 16:47.923
l mean, l'm sorry, but come on.

16:48.091 --> 16:51.259
l think his pants are too tight--

16:52.595 --> 16:55.639
We want the same thing
we wanted with you, Logan:

16:55.807 --> 16:57.140
a weapon.

16:57.308 --> 17:00.477
l'll erase Banner's memories
and reprogram him. ..

17:00.645 --> 17:02.437
...just like l did you.

17:02.605 --> 17:03.855
And then Weapon X. ..

17:04.022 --> 17:07.651
...will have the most powerful creature
on the planet. ..

17:07.819 --> 17:09.778
...at our disposaI.

17:11.531 --> 17:14.407
You should've kiIled me
when you had the chance. ..

17:14.575 --> 17:16.785
...because l'm gonna get out of here...

17:16.953 --> 17:19.121
... l'm gonna kilI all of them. ..

17:19.288 --> 17:22.915
...and then l'm gonna cut out
your heart.

17:25.627 --> 17:29.131
Wolverine, after l'm done with you.. .

17:29.298 --> 17:32.134
...you won't even remember
this conversation.

17:32.301 --> 17:36.805
l've erased your life before,
and l'm going to do it again.

17:36.973 --> 17:41.226
AlI you'll know
is that you belong to Weapon X.. .

17:41.394 --> 17:45.021
...now and forever.

17:47.817 --> 17:49.276
Oh, that is so not cool.

17:51.863 --> 17:53.280
l hate that guy.

17:55.533 --> 17:58.785
Wolverine, you look so sad.

17:58.953 --> 18:02.998
Hey, if it makes you feel any better,
Lady Deathstrike tried to kill you...

18:03.166 --> 18:04.458
...while you were asleep.

18:04.625 --> 18:08.837
-Better than having to listen to you.
-Man, does she hate you.

18:09.005 --> 18:10.505
l mean, we all hate you.. .

18:10.673 --> 18:15.594
...but Deathstrike really, really,
really hates you.

18:15.762 --> 18:19.347
Hey,
stilI have that unbreakable skull?

18:22.018 --> 18:23.602
Damn it.

18:32.028 --> 18:34.988
You will die today, Logan-san.

18:38.826 --> 18:42.954
lt does not matter
what the Professor says.

18:43.122 --> 18:45.832
These are your last breaths.

18:56.177 --> 18:57.886
What are you doing here, Deathstrike?

18:58.054 --> 19:00.722
l'm about to start
Wolverine's reprogramming.

19:00.890 --> 19:02.557
He has to die.

19:02.725 --> 19:06.603
