19:55.278 --> 19:59.489
l'm gonna enjoy killing you for days.

19:59.657 --> 20:04.286
And then l think we'll drop the HuIk
on an orphanage or something...

20:04.453 --> 20:07.038
...just for fun.

20:07.957 --> 20:10.125
Gaijin dog.

20:10.293 --> 20:15.297
For the dishonor you caused
my family, you will suffer.

20:15.464 --> 20:18.466
And then you will die.

20:19.969 --> 20:24.806
Sweetheart, you and your family
can take your honor...

20:24.974 --> 20:28.101
...and shove it up your bony little--

20:30.271 --> 20:32.105
Deathstrike, don't!

21:22.990 --> 21:27.035
Target Iocated in Zone 23.
Take him down.

21:41.550 --> 21:44.052
Backup. We need backup!

21:56.232 --> 21:57.273
WelI, he's alive. ..

21:57.441 --> 22:00.902
...but I think he's gonna need
