23:07.803 --> 23:11.973
So l should just kill you now.
That's what you're saying, right?

23:13.267 --> 23:15.894
Come on, weepy.

23:20.483 --> 23:22.567
You don't know what it's like.

23:22.735 --> 23:24.986
l've been hunted
for as long as I can remember.

23:25.154 --> 23:27.655
And l can't control it. The monster, it--

23:27.823 --> 23:31.326
Bub, do l look like l give a--?

23:50.179 --> 23:52.931
Please, struggle.

23:53.099 --> 23:56.935
lt will make your death
taste so much sweeter.

23:58.437 --> 24:00.313
-No!
-Yes.

24:00.856 --> 24:03.316
As in, "Yes, you're going to die."

24:05.528 --> 24:07.278
